\[\mathcal{B}_{v}=\frac{1}{\frac{1}{\mathcal{B}_{v1}^{1}}+\frac{1}{\mathcal{B}_{v2} }+k_{2}}.\] (16)

Thus, the overall boundary equation can be extended to:

\[\mathcal{B}=\frac{1}{\frac{1}{\mathcal{B}_{p}}+\frac{1}{\mathcal{B}_{v1}^{1}}+ \frac{1}{\mathcal{B}_{v2}}+k_{1}+k_{2}}.\] (17)

